fields.name: Running Shoe Example 1
fields.description: Designed by athletes for athletes, the 4DFWD Running Shoes from adidas feature a premium fit alongside a 3D-printed midsole that works in harmony with the outsole to shift energy forward so you glide through your transition for an effortless ride.

fields.name: Running Shoe Example 2
fields.description: Perform at your best across hard and rocky paths and trails in the TRAILFLY ULTRA G 300 MAX Trail Running Shoes from Inov-8. With an enhanced midsole for responsive cushioning and a max traction outsole for advanced grip on technical terrain.
